productType.productTypeDescription: A garment usually in jersey, having the shape of a T when spread out flat. Usually has a casual look but can be printed, patterned or embellished. It can have a button placket(Henley), but usually has no closure.

productCategories.productcategoryDescription: Description of the front closure of the product

productSubCategory.productSubCategoreyDescription: Fully closed with no buttons, zip or wrap/knot
Full body/Lower body: Full length. Upper body: Starts on hips and below to mid thigh
